    "en": "Then he ordered his sons to prepare for Egypt. So they journeyed until they reached Egypt. They entered upon Yusuf (peace be upon him) and gave him a letter from Ya'qub, seeking his compassion and asking him to return his son. When he looked at it, tears choked him, and he could not bear it, so he stood and entered the house and wept for a while. Then he came out to them and they said to him:",
